1. The CIF files used for the GCMC simulations are included in the CIF_files/ folder. MIL-53_Al.cif is from CCDC database (DI: DOYBEA, solvent has been removed); MIL-100_Fe.cif is from CoRE-MOF 2014 database; the others are from RASPA directory.

2. The GCMC isotherms data is included in isotherm_data/ folder. The organized isotherms data, structure list, and the simulation details are included in isotherm_data_1.xlsx and isotherm_data_2.xlsx.